{"tid":1676453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警fb譴責造謠者無中生有　重申未接新屋嶺性侵投訴","createTime":"2019-10-26T12:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T07:49:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"28ece54cd73452441da771ac4e2a30ffadc045e2","tid":1676453,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191026/s00001/51017551bc2099ca1244de47bcb3c10e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191026%2Fs00001%2F51017551bc2099ca1244de47bcb3c10e.jpg&h=0cd28e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方今晚（26日）在facebook發帖文表示，造謠者除了在香港散播謠言，更在香港以外地方的一個公開場合，訛稱香港警察在新屋嶺扣留中心性侵被捕人士。警方再次強烈譴責有人無中生有，故意抹黑警隊，把完全沒有事實根據的所謂指控不負責任地散播。警方重申，至目前為止，投訴警察課並沒有接獲在新屋嶺扣留中心被性侵的投訴，呼籲公眾切勿胡亂相信謠言。<br />\n<br />\n帖文又標籤「造謠者居心叵測」、「唯恐天下不亂」等。<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒昨日（25日）報道，有戴口罩的香港示威者出席台灣團體主辦的「港鐵太子站追悼牆台灣重建啟動」儀式，聲稱引述一名中學女生的家人，表示該女生在新屋嶺遭4名以上警察輪姦，亦有男生被警察性侵的個案。"},{"pid":"c9f9c0a108517008580ae6d51e7e59f8493a5a0b","tid":1676453,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191026/s00001/1572093965660/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191026%2Fs00001%2F1572093965660%2F&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=3f2a6b6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191026%2Fs00001%2F1572093965660%2F&h=9ec254c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191026/s00001/1572093965660/</a>"},{"pid":"62d304b032c42334aa2d553089e4a370d82cd4c9","tid":1676453,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\